		<news>
[B]Update - v6.7.78 - June 22nd, 2026 [/B]
--[Change] Added support for Collection from MDBList. Add/Remove/View
--[Change] Added official lists from MDBList.
--[Fix] Fix for MDBList Watchlist and Collection pagination.
--[Change] Added support for "dropped" in MDBList.
--[Change] Added support for pause actions on simkl and mdblist.
--[Fix] System service changed to use daemon for users getting shutdown errors.
--[Fix] Reverted change for cloud scrapers from using startwith to in.
--[Fix] Added a fix for tmdb pagination not working correctly after page 1.
--[Change] Added setting for tmdb pagination to be enabled/disabled.
--[Change] MDBList change for refereshing list on episode completion.
--[Change] MDBList episodes in progress no longer uses cache when reloading after watching an episode.
--[Change] Added window property to refresh trakt list after an item removal instead of getting from cache.
--[Change] Added "Finish Watching" for local tracking.
--[Fix] Changed make_settings_dict to use ET instead of minidom.
--[Fix] Change made for updating watch history table when an item has been marked as unwatched.
--[Fix] Correction to make authorizations open the correct settings after authorization is complete. Wrong due to removing 3 sections from settings.
--[Fix] Changes made to allow for download of packs.
--[Change] Changes made to attempt to comply with Trakt 250 item limits.
		</news>
